{"tid":1418903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"打死都唔割、唔割、唔割、一世都唔撚割呀！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T21:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T22:32:14.000Z","uid":135336,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"35bbc54b2b3ac568c0062e4a41ffa1f7f4e252c0","tid":1418903,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:29:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母，前線攞自己嘅青春、自己條命，去賭香港嘅未來 </span></span>，你班企到後一後，索過兩下催淚彈，就post上ig攞光環嘅撚樣，做過啲咩呀？ 場仗都未撚打完，就清算前線，搞分化，有光環你就衝出嚟拎，見勢色唔對路，就急急腳割蓆<br />\n<br />\n講好咗就算玩核彈都唔割蓆㗎嘛，宜家又將前線用完即棄<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你哋係咪想以後都無人肯做前線呀？場仗仲想唔想贏㗎？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對唔住，因為頭先做咗標題黨，所以重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，絕非三毛，三毛死全家"},{"pid":"1456e1592e94d2a9badfb262ef5787e29afcf600","tid":1418903,"uid":6061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:33:28.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割!"},{"pid":"5b72cc30e8aad1dd56f5ba7f64b5d1ed17da473a","tid":1418903,"uid":263951,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:34:07.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個分化五毛撚就比人雞姦爆屎眼(仲要唔落KY)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RHxa8xa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRHxa8xa.png&h=96ca4ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個分化五毛閪就陰道炎流綠色臭西汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ELjMGLA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FELjMGLA.png&h=b440f332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分化前，為左個屎忽！停一停，諗一諗！<br />\n我要你地分化撚五毛狗睇到！！！！"},{"pid":"5b6d429d2bb4db349548f8ee693c2163218268b6","tid":1418903,"uid":135336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:35:15.000Z","msg":"淋病個八婆都唔會同班垃圾割蓆啦，而我嘅前線無私咁奉獻，你班友仲喺度清算義士，你哋仲係咪人嚟？你哋連林鄭都不如呀，屌你老母"},{"pid":"b5f000802d6e75f2226e52f7b1119c938da14685","tid":1418903,"uid":25147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:36:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">都話唔撚割蓆囉 死五毛係咪唔識聽人話</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">玩乜撚都唔割啊</span>"},{"pid":"3bd042cae468dd87068bc0550c073287bedd3d14","tid":1418903,"uid":135336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:37:11.000Z","msg":"平時行動post想話上1000正皮都難，清算義士就咁快上萬，你哋個腦入撚咗水？"},{"pid":"04faa3824f8167b9d7de0affe4e25543c80c1b1e","tid":1418903,"uid":6061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:46:22.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割!"},{"pid":"e3dd79470e60bb6de867f9808c0af90e4b4d1b29","tid":1418903,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:46:55.000Z","msg":"前線快啲入嚟睇下，唔好再睇啲垃圾post去激親自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道你哋睇完一定會喊、覺得好無助、好似俾人出賣咗咁，但唔好氣餒，仲有好多人支持你哋㗎，唔好理班三毛狗，一定要振作，唔可以中佢哋嘅計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58a110ac8712c6cd035b64b4af06b8106240e42","tid":1418903,"uid":119283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:47:06.000Z","msg":"放乜L野彈都唔割"},{"pid":"59235e583743899cf97db1f7f9e00702924efa53","tid":1418903,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:50:31.000Z","msg":"辛苦大家喇！但我想提返你哋一樣嘢！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418774</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&md